1096
00:52:55.532 --> 00:52:59.115
The Gateway Murders, page 68.

1097
00:52:59.198 --> 00:53:02.740
The warehouse scene
with Cora and Mrs. George?


1098
00:53:02.823 --> 00:53:04.323
Do you want me to quote you?

1099
00:53:04.407 --> 00:53:06.073
