Yeah. I usually don't take 'em,


1149
00:56:01.240 --> 00:56:03.448
- but after today...
- Go easy on those.


1150
00:56:03.532 --> 00:56:06.198
I'm serious, we should
keep seeing each other.


1151
00:56:06.282 --> 00:56:09.323
You're the most fun I've had
since Afghanistan.


1152
00:56:09.407 --> 00:56:11.740
You must really
hate me right now.


1153
00:56:11.782 --> 00:56:16.323
I do, very much. But...

1154
00:56:16.407 --> 00:56:18.174
You know that part
about through thick and thin,


1155
00:56:18.198 --> 00:56:19.782
for better or worse?

1156
00:56:19.907 --> 00:56:21.424
You know the part
I'm talking about, right?


1157
00:56:21.448 --> 00:56:23.032
Yeah?

1158
00:56:23.115 --> 00:56:25.365
- What are you saying?
- [Tony] I'm saying,


1159
00:56:25.448 --> 00:56:27.573
we're getting that stuff
out of the way right now,


1160
00:56:27.657 --> 00:56:29.948
and technically, it's not
even our third date yet.


1161
00:56:30.115 --> 00:56:31.657
[chuckling]

1162
00:56:31.740 --> 00:56:33.198
[Sarah]
That is true. We are.


1163
00:56:33.282 --> 00:56:34.573
So what that means is,

1164
00:56:34.657 --> 00:56:37.990
the next 20 years
are gonna be easy.


1165
00:56:38.073 --> 00:56:39.865
♪

1166
00:56:39.948 --> 00:56:41.490
- I hope you're right.
- Mm-hm.


1167
00:56:41.573 --> 00:56:43.573
Oh, oh, oh, oh!

1168
00:56:43.698 --> 00:56:45.490
I'm so sorry... Sorry!

1169
00:56:45.573 --> 00:56:47.448
I'm sorry!

1170
00:56:47.573 --> 00:56:49.990
♪

1171
00:56:50.073 --> 00:56:51.615
I think you've stopped bleeding.

1172
00:56:51.698 --> 00:56:53.198
Oh, I think so too.

1173
00:56:53.282 --> 00:56:55.615
Lemme get it.

1174
00:56:55.740 --> 00:56:58.740
Okay, okay... I got you.

1175
00:56:58.865 --> 00:57:03.657
♪

1176
00:57:03.740 --> 00:57:04.782
Thank you.

1177
00:57:04.865 --> 00:57:05.865
♪

1178
00:57:05.948 --> 00:57:08.407
For what? He got away from me.

1179
00:57:08.448 --> 00:57:11.490
You tried.
And you're here for me.


1180
00:57:11.615 --> 00:57:13.032
That's all that matters.

1181
00:57:13.115 --> 00:57:16.531
♪

1182
00:57:16.532 --> 00:57:18.448
Can I kiss you again
