1183
00:57:18.532 --> 00:57:21.282
Yes. To both questions.

1184
00:57:21.407 --> 00:57:29.407
♪

1185
00:57:31.115 --> 00:57:32.448
[giggles]

1186
00:57:32.532 --> 00:57:34.657
Yeah.
[chuckles]


1187
00:57:34.740 --> 00:57:36.240
- Ouch.
- The pain,


1188
00:57:36.282 --> 00:57:38.490
it was worth it.

1189
00:57:38.573 --> 00:57:39.907
♪

